column5: Not a good day when SDOW DLR FRT and COR are my biggest winners but that is why they are in the portfolio Out of SDOW at 6105 Never know when Nero might change his mind and it turns around and eats your profits alive Besides not risking holding through the weekend Nice gain over two days
